<p class="">I hope that the Debate will be conducted without any personal reflections.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-fc3a204d-c5a4-4bfe-844d-ef0e4dd2b237" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
